Project 2: Weather API Pipeline Automation

Description
For our second project we have collected forecast data from the 5 largest cities in Florida. Using the Open-meteo api data we have extracted, transformed and pushed that data through a pipepline to be used for analysis and forecasting predictions.

Goals:
Gather 7-day forecast data on the weather in Jacksonville, Tampa, St. Petersburg, Miami, and Orlando
Accumulated results into a csv file
Handles errors and logs errors

